name: Yoshiko
description: Nameology series “the science of names” 5 original pieces in the series. Each piece will have 20 copies available. #2/5 - Yoshiko -  Yoshiko is our youngest in the series.  Just a little blossom herself, Yoshiko loves flowers.  Every morning when she wakes up Yoshiko looks out her bedroom window and watches the sunlight dance with the colours of the flower petals.  Original Audio by: Mathmatech
